➜重磅！福州严查电动车违章！交警“入家门、入单位”通报！
http://www.sohu.com/a/430525346_349441	1800
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>重磅！</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>福州行动了</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>针对非机动车闯红灯违法行为人</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>福州交警 部门</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>启动</strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>“上门通报”</strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>程序</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 20px;"><strong><span>“入家门、入单位”</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>进行通报、劝诫</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201109/e366ee4b3f934103a43c4ff514386541.gif" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>如今</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>电动车成为</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>越来越多 <span>福州人代步的工具</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>但</span></strong></span><strong>不少骑手骑车时不遵守交规</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>闯红灯、走机动车道</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>逆行、违规载人、 <span>骑车玩手机等</span></span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>乱象频发</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">陈昊翔/摄</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>接下来</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>交警部门将每天跟踪</strong><strong>曝光</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>闯红灯行为人</strong></span></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
